The Instana Microservices Application Monitoring for PCF provides immediate and granular visibility across all layers of your infrastructure, containers, 
and services. To maximize the velocity and quality of your build and release pipelines, Instana's AutoTrace technology automatically creates observability
and collects health data so your developers can focus on delivering high quality, business critical applications. Instana's PCF Tile helps you: 
* Immediately understand the impact of every release so you can take quick action when deployments go wrong 
* Automatically organize all infrastructure and application data into context rich dependency relationships so you can immediately get to the root cause of any issue
* Confidently deploy software faster with fewer performance and quality defects



