Instana Microservices Application Monitoring includes the following key features:

* Fully automated deployment and management of the Instana Agent across an entire PCF foundation, including VMs spawned by other tiles like Pivotal's RabbitMQ for PCF 
* Self-contained tiled includes agent that has all sensors needed to monitor PCF, its services, and the applications running on it 
* Automated, continuous discovery of all PCF based applications and services



